data.description:
INTERIOR HAS BEEN FULLY REPAINTED TO A NEUTRAL COLOR THROUGHOUT, UPDATED PICTURES COMING SOON. Looking for a spacious home that has been loved and taken care of by its current owners? Well look no further, this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home features multiple dining and living areas. Master bedroom and bath are downstairs, with a separate shower, jetted tub and walk-in closet. Don’t stress there’s a half bath downstairs for your guest as well. Remaining two bedrooms and bathroom are both upstairs. Home sits on a spacious corner lot with a 3 car attached garage. Backyard offers plenty of space for the kids to run, a screened patio with speakers to enjoy will cooking out on these upcoming fall evenings. No HOA. 
Sellers have updated: 
- Roof replaced
- Interior & exterior paint
- Laundry room update/shelving
- Wood accent walls in living room
- Screened patio door replaced
- Pantry door storage install
- Built workbench in garage
- Water heater replaced
- Elevated bookshelf in upstairs bedroom 
- Refrigerator Replaced
- Dishwasher Replaced
- Microwave Replaced
- Washer & Dryer Convey
